locality: 14 km E of Toliara (Tulear) along Route National 7; thorn scrub forest to 3 m tall; Southern (Sud) Domain.

SW Madagascar, Toliara (Tulear) Province, escarpement at the southern end of Lake Tsimanampetsotsa, just above top of ridge. Open scrubby woodland on limestone, with very little soil, with Delonix floribunda and Alluaudia.

SE de Tulear, à 10 km de la RN7 en direction de Saint-Augustin. Fourré épineux xérophile, bas et dense àEuphorbia oncoclada, E. stenoclada et Commiphora sp. Sol squelettique, caillouteux sur calcaire.
N of Toliary, c.3km N of the mouth the Manombo River
